title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully from the table.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export the data in the table.
Expected result: The data should be successfully exported.
Actual result: An exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
